SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – The AM (Acoustic Minds) at Sixth+Main
DESCRIPTION:The AM (Acoustic Minds) will be performing at Sixth+Main on Downtown’s Transit Mall! The AM (Acoustic Minds) is comprised of identical twin sister singers and songwriters Jenni and Amanda Price. (Piano/Guitar/Vocals). They have toured through 11 countries and blend genres of edm\, hip hop\, soul and pop. Known for their songwriting and unique sibling harmonies combined with 80’s synth and heavy bass. \nFor more information\, CLICK HERE.
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-the-am-acoustic-minds-at-sixthmain-3/
