SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – Reisender at Big Pink
DESCRIPTION:Reisender will be performing at Big Pink on Downtown’s Transit Mall!! \nReisender is the musical endeavor of west-coast songwriter & multi-instrumentalist Paul Conroy. With influences ranging from Paul Simon to The Flaming Lips\, Conroy crafts upbeat\, moody\, and eclectic synth & guitar-driven indie-pop anthems. Having performed alongside national artists including Drake Bell\, Eisley\, and Hippo Campus\, Reisender has toured across the western US as well as in Europe and Korea\, and boasts both an international and local following. His single “Generation 1099” has been described as “a seriously replay-worthy track” by the Bay Bridged\, and his 2021 Album Fmly as “an indie/alt festival-ready collection of gems” by FourCulture. Reisender is currently based in Portland\, OR with a lineup comprising Paul Conroy and his cousin Ben Stager on drums. \n 
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-reisender-at-big-pink/
LOCATION:Big Pink\, 111 SW 5th Ave #1250\, Portland\, OR\, 97204\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Reisender_PaulConroy.png
END:VEVENT
