SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – Jet Black Pearl at Pendleton
DESCRIPTION:Accordionist and flautist Jet Black Pearl will be performing at Pendleton Pioneer Place on Downtown’s Transit Mall! Jet Black Pearl’s smartly wacky songs sound like a mad hatter’s European tea party with a funky attitude. Before your very eyes\, she creates grooves and loops of flute\, plastic bottles\, rubber pigs\, vocal percussion and harmonies\, while squeezing her red accordion. She also might do a little dance for you. \nFor more information\, CLICK HERE.
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-jet-black-pearl-at-pendleton/
