SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – Kendall Lujan at Less and More Coffee
DESCRIPTION:Kendal Lujan will be performing at Less and More Coffee on Downtown’s Transit Mall! \nPortland\, Oregon based artist\, Kendall Lujan embarks on her first full length album “Lucky Penny’ it is set to be released Fall 2024. ‘Lucky Penny’ features many genres Including Jazz\, Folk\,  Bosa Nova and Indie-Rock. Her writing is real\, introspective and reflective. After touring the songs in Europe twice this past Fall Lujan is ready to show her versatility and growth as an artist. The first single to be released late March 2024 titled ‘Goodbyes’. Lujan is set to tour Germany\, Austria\, and Switzerland again fall 2024 with a full band.
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-kendall-lujan-at-less-and-more-coffee-2/
LOCATION:Less & More Coffee\, 1003 SW 5th Ave\, Portland\, OR\, 97204\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/k-31-scaled.jpeg
