SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – Sadie Gregg at Pioneer Place
DESCRIPTION:Opera singer Sadie Gregg will be performing at Pioneer Place in front of Saint Laurent on Downtown’s Transit Mall! Sadie Gregg has been commended by the press as “a mezzo-soprano with a rich\, flexible instrument\,” and as “a standout” whose “amber-toned mezzo-soprano sounded strong across her full range.” Performances include Seattle Opera\, Portland Opera\, Boston Lyric Opera\, Odyssey Opera\, Oregon Mahler Festival\, Tualatin Valley Symphony\, and Bravo! Concerts Northwest. \nFor more information\, CLICK HERE. \n 
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-sadie-gregg-at-pioneer-place/
LOCATION:Pioneer Place Main Entrance\, 700 SW 5th Ave\, Portland\, OR\, 97204\, United States
