SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – Tyler Waltner Trio at Sixth+Main
DESCRIPTION:The Tyler Waltner Trio will be performing at Sixth+Main on Downtown’s Transit Mall! The Tyler Waltner Trio plays heavy blues\, swing\, bebop\, hard-bop\, Latin\, funk\, and modern jazz influenced tunes featuring complex rhythms and abstract harmonies to put together a unique fabric of music\, sound\, and textures that only a fraction of musicians their age can accomplish. \nFor more information\, CLICK HERE. \n\n\n\n 
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-tyler-waltner-trio-at-sixthmain-2/
