SUMMARY:In Concert on Downtown’s Transit Mall – Ben Grace at Big Pink
DESCRIPTION:Ben Grace will be performing at Big Pink on Downtown’s Transit Mall! \nAt the center of Australian singer-songwriter Ben Grace’s impeccably crafted songs is a story of undoing. Drawn by the roots-driven tradition of Americana to sing the stories that need to be told\, Ben’s music hovers in the space between lightness and the depths\, wrestling its way through humor and melody to peel back the layers and reveal the naked truth of us. Through the specificity of his own deconstruction\, Ben writes into our universal search for belonging\, spiritual homecoming\, and desire to live seen and unashamed. \nFor more information\, CLICK HERE. \n 
URL:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/event/in-concert-on-downtowns-transit-mall-ben-grace-at-big-pink/
LOCATION:Big Pink\, 111 SW 5th Ave #1250\, Portland\, OR\, 97204\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.thesquarepdx.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Ben-Grace.webp
END:VEVENT
